expression: stdout
---
Show device status and telemetry

Usage: wheelctl device status [OPTIONS] <DEVICE>

Arguments:
  <DEVICE>  Device ID or name

Options:
      --json        Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -w, --watch       Watch status in real-time
  -v, --verbose...  Verbose logging
  -h, --help        Print help
